  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a pressure cooker over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the garlic and saut\u00023 until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add the rice and cook, stirring constantly, for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the chicken broth, thyme, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the dried figs and stir to combine.",
    "Lock the lid and cook at high pressure for 4 minutes.",
    "Let the pressure release naturally for 10 minutes, then quick-release any remaining pressure.",
    "Stir in the Greek yogurt and chopped parsley.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
